{
  "chapter": 41,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十一回\"流浪江湖\"，小鱼儿与花无缺在秋夜对峙，小鱼儿痛陈花无缺虽完美无缺却毫无情感体验，花无缺坦然承认。铁心兰为救小鱼儿当众脱衣紧紧抱住花无缺，迫使花无缺无法动手，小鱼儿趁机逃离。小鱼儿在稻田中自省，深感自己空有聪明而无真本事，随后加入长江边的\"海家班\"戏班子，化名\"海小呆\"翻筋斗谋生。海四爹豪爽收留他，其幼女海红珠对小鱼儿暗生情愫。不久小鱼儿在江岸重见花无缺一行人，铁心兰面上幸福的光彩令他嫉妒如焚。海红珠失落时从绳索上跌落，白凌霄和李明生仗义出头却意图轻薄海红珠，小鱼儿挺身而出，一掌击退李明生、重创白凌霄后再度离去。海红珠痛哭追呼，海四爹叹道小鱼儿不属于他们这群人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，你装得很像，但无论如何，我还是要你的命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你知道么，你'无缺'这名儿的确取得很好，你的确没有什么缺憾……你出身于世上名声最响的武林圣地，你少年英俊，不虑钱财，你的武功可使江湖中每一个人都对你恭恭敬敬，你的美貌、谈吐和风韵，又可使天下每一个少女都为你着迷，你的名誉也无懈可击，令人甚至在背后都不能骂你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "天下若真有一个完美无缺的人，那人就是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "多谢夸奖。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但我却忽然发觉，你还是少了样情感。你彻头彻尾是个没有情感的人，你身上流的血，只怕都是冷的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "是么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你不服么？好，我问你，你可真的懂得什么叫爱，什么叫恨？你可曾尝过爱的滋味？恨的滋味？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你甚至连烦恼都没有，老、病、愁闷、贫苦、失望、悲伤、羞侮、恼怒……这些本是全人类都不能避免的痛苦！但你却一样也没有……一个完全没有痛苦的人，又怎能真正领略到欢乐的滋味。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你既没有真正爱过一个人，也没有真正恨过一个人，你没有痛苦，也没有欢乐……别人也许都羡慕你，我却觉得你活着实在没有什么意思。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "也许你说得不错，这只怕也是我从小的环境造成的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，只有'移花宫'才能造出你这样的人，使你变成一个活动的木头人。你虽然对每个人都谦恭有礼，但心里却绝不会认为他们值得尊敬，你虽然对每个女孩子都温柔体贴，但也绝不是真的喜欢她们。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "就算你要杀人，你心里都未必认为他是该杀的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这的确是遗憾得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，现在我话已说完了，你只管动手吧，我倒要看看，你到底能在几招内将我杀死！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可要使用兵器？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我没有兵器。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若愿使用兵器，我可以陪你到有兵器的地方，让你选择一样。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你明明知道我纵有武器，也非你敌手，你明明要杀死我，还要对我如此客气，若是别人，必定要认为你是个阴险毒辣的人，但我却知道你不是，因为你连虚伪作假都不会，因为你根本不必作假。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你实在很了解我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你再想找一个这么了解你的人，只怕很难了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我不要用兵器，你动手吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这样的天气……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这样的天气，的确很适于杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的天气，只令我觉得冷得很……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你看我美么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你……你为什么要……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "死人，你……你还站在这里？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这样……你还不走？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你再不走，我就死在你面前！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "老爷子，我也跟着你走江湖好么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "走江湖可不是好玩的，要有本事，还得不怕吃苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "翻筋斗？干咱们这行的谁不会翻筋斗，翻筋斗原是最简单的玩意儿……野犊子，你就翻几个让他瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ye_du_zi",
      "text": "你最多能翻几个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_du_zi",
      "speaker_name": "野犊子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "大概二三十个吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_ye_du_zi",
      "text": "但我却可以翻一两百个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "哦！能一口气翻八十个筋斗的人，我少年时倒见着一个，那就是李家班李老大，自从他挨了一刀后，就再没有别人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "但我却能翻一百六十个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若真能翻一百六十个……不，只要能翻八十个筋斗，这行饭就能吃上个一辈子了，虽没有什么好的吃，但也有酒有肉。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "够了没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "够了，够了……太够了，快跟着野犊子上船去。洗个脸，换件衣裳，等着吃宵夜吧。从今天起，你就是咱们海家班的人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "我爹爹妈妈刚死没多久，我在他们坟前发过誓，为他们守三年丧，我……我发誓说这三年绝不洗脸。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "可怜的孩子，想不到你还这么孝顺……我的孩子们叫我四爹，以后，你也叫我四爹吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你既然不理我，为何又吃了我的橘子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "我不会说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不会说话？你难道是哑巴？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "我不配和你说话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不配，谁说你不配？……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "别人都叫你小呆，但我却知道你是聪明人。不但聪明，而且比别人都要聪明得多，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我知道你的身世一定有很多秘密，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你认得他们？……我知道，你原来是属于他们那一群人的，绝不会属于我们……我们，只不过是一群卑贱而可怜的人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我现在才知道你为什么不理我，只因我不配和你说话，是么？我又怎比得上那两个女孩子，她们是那么高贵，而我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kan_ke_yi",
      "speaker_name": "看客甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还瞧什么，这小妞儿今天心不在焉，只怕已在想汉子了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kan_ke_er",
      "speaker_name": "看客乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，小姑娘想谁呀，是在想我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ling_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "白凌霄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁若再对这位姑娘说出一个无礼的字，我就割下他的舌头！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老子就挖出他的眼睛！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_bai_ling_xiao",
      "text": "多谢少爷仗义。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ling_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "白凌霄",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "这也没什么！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "这可足够买几十坛酒了，爷儿为什么赏你银子，你总该明白。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "红丫头，还不快过来道谢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_bai_ling_xiao",
      "text": "谢谢少爷……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "咱们的大哥喜欢你，你陪他去喝两杯吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "咱们这孩子年纪还小，等过两年再让她陪少爷喝酒去。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "过两年？大爷已等不及了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_du_zi",
      "speaker_name": "野犊子",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "你放开她！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "谁也不能将她带走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这脏小子，想找死么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好了，杀人了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小呆……小呆……等等我……等等我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他走了……我知道他永远也不会回来了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "他虽然不会回来了，但这也是没法子的……他本就不属于这一群，你又有什么法子拉住他……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "但我……我不能……求求你老人家……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "你只有忍耐，像这样的人，非但我拉不住他，世上……世上只怕没有任何人能拉住他的……你只怕是永远再也见不着他了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    }
